msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/spellcasting/spells/private_sanctum.md:8
msgid "# Private Sanctum _4th-level abjuration_"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/spellcasting/spells/private_sanctum.md:13
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Casting Time:** 10 minutes   \n"
"**Range:** 120 feet    \n"
"**Components:** V, S, M (a thin sheet of lead, a piece of opaque glass, a "
"wad of cotton or cloth, and powdered chrysolite)   \n"
"**Duration:** 24 hours \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/spellcasting/spells/private_sanctum.md:16
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"You make an area within range magically secure. The area is a cube that can "
"be as small as 5 feet to as large as 100 feet on each side. The spell lasts "
"for the duration or until you use an action to dismiss it.    \n"
"When you cast the spell, you decide what sort of security the spell "
"provides, choosing any or all of the following properties:\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: sources/spellcasting/spells/private_sanctum.md:23
msgid "Sound can't pass through the barrier at the edge of the warded area."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: sources/spellcasting/spells/private_sanctum.md:23
msgid ""
"The barrier of the warded area appears dark and foggy, preventing vision "
"(including darkvision) through it."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: sources/spellcasting/spells/private_sanctum.md:23
msgid ""
"Sensors created by divination spells can't appear inside the protected area "
"or pass through the barrier at its perimeter."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: sources/spellcasting/spells/private_sanctum.md:23
msgid "Creatures in the area can't be targeted by divination spells."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: sources/spellcasting/spells/private_sanctum.md:23
msgid "Nothing can teleport into or out of the warded area."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: sources/spellcasting/spells/private_sanctum.md:23
msgid "Planar travel is blocked within the warded area."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/spellcasting/spells/private_sanctum.md:25
msgid ""
"Casting this spell on the same spot every day for a year makes this effect "
"permanent."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/spellcasting/spells/private_sanctum.md:26
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**At Higher Levels.** When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 5th "
"level or higher, you can increase the size of the cube by 100 feet for each "
"slot level beyond 4th. Thus you could protect a cube that can be up to 200 "
"feet on one side by using a spell slot of 5th level. \n"
msgstr ""
